name: Soul II
description:
E҉s҉s҉e҉n҉t҉i҉a҉l҉ ҉M҉e҉a҉n҉i҉n҉g҉ ҉o҉f҉ ҉s҉o҉u҉l҉:҉

     1: The spiritual part of a person that is believed to give
     life to the body and in many religions is believed to live
     forever.

     2: A person's deeply felt moral and emotional nature.

     3: The ability of a person to feel kindness and sympathy
     for others, to appreciate beauty and art, and many more.
